{"tid":507073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚野後期/未世聖徒教會？","createTime":"2017-12-22T22:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T06:44:00.000Z","uid":127477,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc2d2f64e0a2c08f1b9a932c4d9787ab8e20146","tid":507073,"uid":127477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T22:31:41.000Z","msg":"有個朋友係返後期聖徒教會，份人真係好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪返呢個教會返得多<br />\n定係個份人本身係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如我係地下發現左條金鏈/貴重野，佢老母條撚樣係我手上拎走，話要拎去警處<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講到明話想自己袋（我認貪心）<br />\n「屌，一條金鏈幾千蚊好平咋，自己買條帶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我屌你老母真係吹撚漲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw條友無正職/散工/差唔多拎綜緩個堆<br />\n唔解釋咁多，總然之好假，問題得一個，關唔關教會事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後唔知佢係咪真係拎左去警處<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0185b53a9dbc4c0d59410f67d0b39df606bf167","tid":507073,"uid":127477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:57:42.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc6b635768b9316db06b4c77d082e86e72ea65f","tid":507073,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"好似係你柒多D"},{"pid":"0d2e823383ff3a7eb059da7c291334c14da58784","tid":507073,"uid":127477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係你柒多D</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}